Summary: spinning passing east to south, between trees
divs: Sighting Detailswindow by the bed: I woke and looked out to see object; woke wife who confirmed sight. It was spinning clockwise: outer shell spinning round a center (spinning part was faint brown; center silver). Object passed between trees.50.0.0 to 210.0.0. This is actually my second report of this event; I always felt that first report may not have been received and I have been meaning to repeat report. Sorry that it took so long. Back in 1992, I told Marge Christersen about sighting.
